Features
--------
Command to open user list in editor (git config --edit --file ~/.gitsu)
Colorize output when it's configured
Make default scope configurable
Support multiple users at once

Bugs
-------
Make it so that you can't do more than one of clear/add/switch at once
When I type 'git su -c', I see
    fatal: unable to read config file '/etc/gitconfig': No such file or directory
